## Original Paper and Repository

This project is based on the following paper and repository:

**Paper**: "Addressing Heterophily in Graph Anomaly Detection: A Perspective of Graph Spectrum" (WWW2023)

**Original Authors**: Yuan Gao, Xiang Wang, Xiangnan He, Zhenguang Liu, Huamin Feng, Yongdong Zhang

**Original Repository**: 
- [GHRN](https://github.com/squareRoot3/Rethinking-Anomaly-Detection)
- [GADBench](https://github.com/squareRoot3/GADBench)

The original code and paper are subject to their respective licenses. Please refer to the original repositories for license information.

